    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for model risk level 3. The single shortfall in Test conditions (achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) was reviewed and accepted by the team on the basis that the single-condition ASTM F1717 protocol is the regulatory standard and that multi-condition characterisation is planned for the next assessment cycle. Overall simulation credibility is judged sufficient to support the intended regulatory submission.",
